  "prompt": "Where can I buy Soju in mumbai?",
  "response": "In Mumbai, you can find Soju at various locations, including liquor stores, supermarkets, and Asian specialty stores. Some notable places to check include:\n\n1. **Nature's Basket**: Various outlets across Mumbai, known for stocking international alcohol brands.\n2. **Living Liquidz**: Multiple locations in Mumbai, offering a wide selection of liquors including imported ones.\n3. **30Down**: Located in Khar, this store may carry Soju among other spirits.\n4. **Foodhall**: Located in various parts of Mumbai, this high-end supermarket has a good selection of international alcohol brands.\n\nAdditionally, some Korean restaurants and bars in Mumbai may also serve Soju, allowing you to enjoy it on the premises. Always call ahead to check availability before making a trip.",
